headline: Textron Aviation Defense and Thai Aviation Industries Sign Agreement to Support Royal Thai Air Force
summary: PARIS, June 19, 2025--Textron Aviation Defense and Thai Aviation Industries sign MOA to sustain Beechcraft T-6TH and AT-6TH aircraft for the Royal Thai Air Force (RTAF)
